  15:app_statemachine.c ****  *
  16:app_statemachine.c ****  * HFSM engine: parent table, LCA walk, transition driver, error raiser.
  17:app_statemachine.c ****  *
  18:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ROOT
  19:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├─ STBY ── STBY_DEFER (boot)
  20:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── STBY_HOLD
  21:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├─ MANU ── MANU_JOYSTICK
  22:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├─ AUTO ── AUTO_HOME*
  23:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── ACQ_GPS*
  24:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── ACQ_SPIRAL*
  25:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── TRACKING*
  26:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── LOSS*
  27:app_statemachine.c ****  *   ├       ── NO_LOCK*
  28:app_statemachine.c ****  *   └─ ERROR ─ ERROR_ACTIVE
  29:app_statemachine.c ****  * 
  30:app_statemachine.c ****  *      * = declared, not yet implemented
  31:app_statemachine.c ****  *
  32:app_statemachine.c ****  * KEYMAP (keep in sync with the key_* handlers in section 5):
  33:app_statemachine.c ****  *   GLOBAL (any non-FATAL leaf):
  34:app_statemachine.c ****  *     k       soft kill -> STBY_HOLD
  35:app_statemachine.c ****  *     [       capture origin from telemetry
  36:app_statemachine.c ****  *     ?       help
  37:app_statemachine.c ****  *     Ctrl+R  clear FATAL latch -> STBY_HOLD
  38:app_statemachine.c ****  *   NAV (suppressed where leaf_traps_nav()==1):
  39:app_statemachine.c ****  *     1/2/3   STBY_HOLD / MANU_JOYSTICK / AUTO
  40:app_statemachine.c ****  *   MANU_JOYSTICK leaf:
  41:app_statemachine.c ****  *     r/a     RATE / ABSOLUTE      e  exit -> STBY_HOLD
  42:app_statemachine.c ****  *     ]       -> AUTO_HOME
  43:app_statemachine.c ****  *
  44:app_statemachine.c ****  * DISPATCH PRECEDENCE (app_dispatch_key):
  45:app_statemachine.c ****  *     FATAL-lockout  >  global  >  leaf  >  nav
  46:app_statemachine.c **** */
